CONTEXT.md
BOOKMARKS.md
CV-*.pdf
companies/**
!companies/
!companies/*/
!companies/**/.gitkeep

# Notion queue (transient)
notion_queue/
notion_queue_results/

# Scan results (personal)
scan_results/**
!scan_results/.gitkeep
Bookmarks
